Source: I001 and `docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-17-quota-presentation-policy.md`, Task 5.

Add a cross-caller seam regression, remove `visibleWindows`, `primaryWindows`, and `extraWindows` from `QuotaCommon.js`, refocus visibility tests on configuration, and run the complete serial suite.

Acceptance: no rendering/library caller contains the old selectors, every surface crosses `QuotaPresentation.presentProfile()`, Node and shell tests pass, Qt Quick tests explicitly pass in a functioning Qt environment, and the design acceptance criteria are reviewed.